---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About AI Automation Agencies Directory">
  <Header />
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
      AI Automation Agencies Directory is a curated marketplace for businesses that need Zapier, Make.com, and n8n professionals.
      We connect teams with agencies and freelancers that can design workflows, build automations, and operate reliable automation stacks.
    </p>
    <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mt-6">
      The directory started as a static SEO-first reference and is now being expanded into an ops-ready lead platform.
      We focus on transparent listing quality, practical lead routing, and trust signals for both agencies and clients.
    </p>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
